{"tid":195380,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母又係陳詠謙你條撚屌","createTime":"2017-04-10T14:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T15:52:02.000Z","uid":1779,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b461c8df4421cd6c58a17145247ea4e77543cb","tid":195380,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"晏就聽聽下電台播下d派台歌<br />\n聽到乜 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得我是零~~</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到屌出聲 屌你老母有冇搞撚錯呀 乜撚野歌詞來㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一search原來又係陳詠謙你條垃圾既杰作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母成撚日填詞填到九唔撚搭八<br />\n喂講真好多歌詞未必成首都用字精煉 <br />\n但唔會un耳到破壞哂成首詞囉<br />\n你老母 一句咩王非的孤寂多麼孤寂 已經破撚壞柏宇首歌<br />\n依首 你覺得我是零直頭垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆你個街你會考al中文係咪拎U㗎<br />\n幾時先肯收皮呀陳詠謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb16cd9204e0fadeee0a87cbe384d472c55dd1a","tid":195380,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a50e44d420ed5af14e0f91179160c3e650bf93c","tid":195380,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"你快樂過生活 我拼命去生存<br />\n真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"61ecc7f101cc5bf495fef47c3c7c2e8935b9115c","tid":195380,"uid":92376,"like":0,"disl